      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in extraordinary, mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless with a deep luster, free of any chips or scratches, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh state. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, reflecting its history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly immaculate example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
